To celebrate Black History Month going into Women’s History Month, I partnered with Martell to create a trunk highlighting some Phenomenal products from black female owned companies to gift to some phenomenal women who continuously are making strides in their respective fields.

I toast you & honor you ladies, And I hope you enjoy your gift. #MakeYourStatement 💜 

Products Included: @coolcoffeeclique, @labeautyologist, @shopherlistic, @sosheargenius, @thecrayoncase, @itsbrowngirljane & @culturetags

Visit www.fearless.fund and click on VC Week to get your in-person or virtual tickets!
